metadata.name: Rare Precious Skull
metadata.description: Captain Jack and his crew set out to search for a rumored sunken ship filled with treasure in the Bermuda Triangle. They discovered a human skull decorated with diamonds, rubies, emeralds, and sapphires and retrieved it from the water. As they searched the area further, they found more and more valuable treasures. When the sun rose, they had amassed a hoard of glittering jewels and precious metals. They returned home as heroes and the rare treasures they had discovered became the talk of the town. The captain and his crew were hailed as the greatest treasure hunters of their time and their discovery in the Bermuda Triangle went down in history as one of the most exciting and valuable finds ever made.
